    <description>
        <p>An unofficial desktop client for Canvas LMS, including features such as:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Downloading course content, files and videos</li>
            <li>Viewing content while offline</li>
            <li>Viewing course mail/announcements</li>
            <li>Highlighting new content</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To use the Breeze theme on KDE, go to Options &gt; Theme and select "Native"
        </p>
